\myparagraph{Limitations of existing ConvQA benchmarks} Notable efforts at ConvQA benchmarking like QuAC [choi2018quac] (text), CoQA [reddy2019coqa] (text), SQA [iyyer2017search] (tables), ConvQuestions [christmann2019look] (KB), and CSQA [saha2018complex] (KB) assume a single answering source. Rather than the easier option of artificially augmenting any of these with heterogeneous inputs,